snippet.title: LAZA KNITEZ!! - out now on PC/MAC
snippet.description: LAZA KNITEZ!! is a fast-paced jousting deathmatch game for up to 4 players. Teleport to the neon-lit ALL CAPS technofuture and challenge your friends to mind-blowing hypercombat. Fire your laser-lance from a distance, get up close and personal to empale your foes and use 7 different power-ups to your tactical advantage.
